      <div class="pp-feature" style="--wc:#c89a3a;"><span class="pp-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('grid') }}</span><b>13 formats, one call</b><span>From stand-up pouches to retort packs to spouted formats — you don't need multiple suppliers.</span></div>
      <div class="pp-feature" style="--wc:#7a8a6c;"><span class="pp-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('flask') }}</span><b>Compliance-ready films</b><span>Food-grade, pharma-approved, agrochemical-tough. The right barrier for the right shelf.</span></div>
